---
import OriginalLayout from '../layouts/OriginalLayout.astro';
import '../styles/original/guidedreading.css';
---
<OriginalLayout title="Guided Reading – SOS Magic" page="guidedreading">
<main class="guided-page">
    <section class="guided-section">

      <div class="guided-kicker">
        <span class="guided-line-big" data-text="Guided Reading">Guided Reading</span>
      </div>

      <p class="guided-text guided-intro">
        Your 24/7 online navigation to stop the mental spiral and regain control.
      </p>

      <div class="guided-video" aria-label="Guided Reading video">
        <div class="guided-video-shell">
          <video class="guided-player"
                 src="https://sosmagic.b-cdn.net/videos/reading.mp4"
                 poster="https://sosmagic.b-cdn.net/videos/reading.jpeg"
                 controls
                 playsinline
                 preload="metadata" aria-label="Page introduction video"></video>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="guided-text">
        The Neon Tarot, Oracle, and Angelic message decks used in Guided Readings don’t just predict life’s storms ahead.
      </p>

      <p class="guided-text">
        They act as the compass of your intuition, helping you weather any storm and come out on top.
      </p>

      <div class="guided-cta-wrap">
        <a class="guided-cta" href="/">Get Clarity</a>
      </div>

    </section>
  </main>

</OriginalLayout>
